"type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"also named “RGAA”."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The WCAG specifications, for AA level, defines a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define whether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","kind":"identifier"}]},"https://accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr":{"identifier":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr","title":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","type":"link","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Référentiel Général d’Amélioration de l’Accessibilité","type":"text"}],"url":"https:\/\/accessibilite.numerique.gouv.fr"},"doc://OUDSFoundations/documentation/OUDSFoundations":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Contains a set of helpers and extensions shared for higher level targets."}],"title":"Foundations","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentatio